                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">When Victims Become Killers: Colonialism, Nativism, and the</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
